name: Read Description Before You Start: Panel Rules & Guidelines for a Smooth Experience
category: Read Description Before You Start: Panel Rules & Guidelines for a Smooth Experience
description:
📜 Rules & Terms

𝐇𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐨 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐂𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐬,

Welcome to 𝐌𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐟𝐬𝐦𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐥.𝐢𝐧 | 𝐓𝐨𝐩𝐬𝐦𝐦.𝐢𝐧.

This is a system that generates things automatically. There can be system errors sometimes.

We don\t create accounts | This website is not for creating accounts.

We cannot manipulate any of your data since we are using a rental panel. So, if you need a refill or refund, there are certain rules.

We\ve been running this panel since 2019 and have been in the business since 2017. Rest assured, your funds are 100% safe with us, and we guarantee fair and transparent services. Below are important guidelines to keep in mind when using our services:

General Rules ✅
By making a new order or creating an account, you automatically accept our Terms & Conditions.

Make sure your Followers, Subscribers, Likes, Comments, and View Counters are not hidden. Your account must be Public, not Private, before placing an order.

If your account or posts/reels are set to Private/Hidden, or if posts are deleted, the order will be marked as Completed, and no refund will be provided.

Do not place more than one order on the same link at the same time until the first order is completed.

Do not place orders for Pornography, Politics, Extremism, or any content that stirs public opinion.

If you face any payment issue, don’t worry. Just message us on WhatsApp—your money is 100% safe with us.

Once funds are added, they cannot be refunded to your bank. Funds will remain in your topsmm.in account for service usage only.

Paytm Usage: Using our Paytm details for accepting payments on your own website is strictly prohibited.

We cannot deduct your funds without your concern. The only way is through service deductions. You can verify your balance anytime on the Payments Page.

Any attempt of fraud, fund manipulation, abuse, or threatening behavior towards our support team will result in account suspension.

Do not change accounts from Public to Private after placing an order. Such orders will be marked as completed with no refunds or cancellations.

Refill Policy 🔄
No refill will be provided if you change your username or make your account Private.

Refill applies to Order ID only, not for links. If your link doesn’t work, we cannot refill.

Condition 1: Refill is calculated as Start Count + Order Quantity = End Count. Example: If your start count is 1000 and you order 1000 followers, you are eligible for a refill if your count drops below 2000, provided it stays above the original 1000. Each order is reviewed separately.

Refill requests may be rejected if the drop is less than 10%, as our system only counts drops above 10%.

If you ordered followers and they drop, please use the Refill Button on the Orders Page or contact us on WhatsApp. Do not place a new order until the first one is completely refilled, otherwise, you may receive fewer followers.

Refill period may vary depending on updates or overload. Usually, it is processed within 24–72 hours. During Instagram updates, refill may take longer—please be patient until stability returns.

Condition 2: If your account already has a large follower base (e.g., 10K) and you order a smaller amount (e.g., 1K), old followers may drop naturally. We cannot refill in such cases. Please order your complete requirement from us so we can track and refill properly.

No refills will be provided for 50K–1M base accounts if the order is less than 30% of the existing count. Example: If you have 1M followers, you must order at least 300K+ from the same provider. Do not split orders across different providers.

No refills for Flagged for Review profiles or No-Post profiles.

Refills are guaranteed only if followers drop from the End Count (Start + Ordered Quantity), subject to these conditions:

No refill if drop is less than 10% of the order.

No refill if username is changed.

No refill if followers are mixed from other providers.

Refund Policy 💰
No refund if you place the same order on topsmm.in and another panel simultaneously for the same link. We do not support or encourage this.

If you place an order with wrong or non-working links, it will be automatically canceled and refunded to your topsmm.in wallet balance.

Partial = Refund for the undelivered portion. Example: If you order 1000 and receive 500, 50% of the payment will be refunded.

Canceled = Full refund. If an order is canceled, the full amount will be refunded to your wallet.

Refund requests for running orders may be possible for some services, but not for fast-working services.

If an order is marked Completed, you must report any issue within 24 hours for a possible solution.

For No Refill Services, no refunds or refills will be given, whether delivered, partially delivered, or marked complete.

During Instagram updates, only partial refunds may be provided. Refills may take longer.

Username switching tricks to claim refills will not work. Accounts caught attempting this will be banned immediately.

This is a multi-vendor platform; system errors may occur. Please deal with them calmly and always read our T&C.

Important Notes 📌
Do not click on potential spam notifications on Instagram about removing fake/spam accounts. If you do, and followers drop, it will not be our responsibility. No refills will be provided in such cases. Inform your clients as well. A 100% drop is not possible with our old account services.

Always keep all order IDs linked to the same account handy when requesting refills. Submit complete details to avoid delays.

For Live Views, always take screenshots with time, username, and count visible. Fake documents will result in immediate account suspension.

Behavior Policy 🚫
Any abuse, threats, or misbehavior with our support team will result in permanent account suspension.

About Our Platform ℹ️

topsmm.in is a multi-vendor reseller platform, providing services from different providers.

We operate as a mediator, reselling services with a small margin.

We are not responsible for social media account creation or content policies.

Provider details are never disclosed due to security reasons.

For any queries, please raise a support ticket or contact us on WhatsApp.


सामान्य नियम ✅
नया ऑर्डर करने या अकाउंट बनाने का मतलब है कि आप हमारी Terms & Conditions को मान चुके हैं।

👉 सुनिश्चित करें कि आपके Followers, Subscribers, Likes, Comments और View Counters छुपे न हों। आपका अकाउंट Public होना चाहिए, Private नहीं।

👉 अगर आपका अकाउंट या पोस्ट/रील Private/Hidden कर दिया जाता है, या पोस्ट डिलीट कर दिए जाते हैं, तो ऑर्डर को Completed मान लिया जाएगा और कोई रिफंड नहीं मिलेगा।

👉 एक ही लिंक पर एक समय में एक से ज्यादा ऑर्डर न लगाएँ, जब तक पहला ऑर्डर पूरा न हो जाए।

👉 Pornography, Politics, Extremism या Public Opinion भड़काने वाले कंटेंट पर ऑर्डर न करें।

👉 अगर कोई पेमेंट इश्यू आता है तो टेंशन न लें, बस हमें WhatsApp पर मैसेज करें। आपका पैसा 100% सुरक्षित है।

👉 एक बार फंड जोड़ने के बाद उन्हें बैंक में रिफंड नहीं किया जा सकता। ये सिर्फ आपके topsmm.in वॉलेट में रहेंगे और सेवाओं में उपयोग होंगे।

👉 Paytm Usage: हमारे Paytm डिटेल्स का अपनी वेबसाइट पर पेमेंट लेने के लिए इस्तेमाल करना सख्त मना है।

👉 बिना आपकी जानकारी के हम आपके फंड्स डिडक्ट नहीं कर सकते। फंड्स सिर्फ सर्विस डिडक्शन के जरिए ही कटेंगे। आप Payments पेज पर अपना बैलेंस कभी भी चेक कर सकते हैं।

👉 किसी भी तरह का Fraud, Fund Manipulation, Abuse या सपोर्ट टीम को धमकी देने पर आपका अकाउंट Suspend कर दिया जाएगा।

👉 ऑर्डर लगाने के बाद अकाउंट को Public से Private न करें। ऐसे ऑर्डर Completed मान लिए जाएंगे और कोई रिफंड/कैंसिलेशन नहीं मिलेगा।

Refill Policy 🔄
👉 अगर आप Username बदलते हैं या अकाउंट Private करते हैं तो कोई Refill नहीं मिलेगा।

👉 Refill सिर्फ Order ID पर लागू होता है, लिंक पर नहीं। अगर लिंक काम नहीं करता तो Refill नहीं मिलेगा।

👉 Condition 1: Refill इसी फॉर्मूले पर आधारित है → Start Count + Order Quantity = End Count.
उदाहरण: अगर Start Count 1000 है और आपने 1000 Followers का ऑर्डर दिया है तो Refill तभी मिलेगा जब आपका काउंट 2000 से नीचे चला जाए (लेकिन 1000 से ऊपर रहना चाहिए)।

👉 Refill रिक्वेस्ट रिजेक्ट हो सकती है अगर Drop 10% से कम है।

👉 अगर आपके Followers Drop होते हैं, तो Orders पेज पर Refill बटन दबाएँ या WhatsApp पर संपर्क करें। नया ऑर्डर न लगाएँ जब तक पहला Refill पूरा न हो जाए।

👉 Refill समय 24–72 घंटे तक ले सकता है। अगर Instagram पर Update चल रहा हो तो इससे भी ज्यादा समय लग सकता है, कृपया धैर्य रखें।

👉 Condition 2: अगर आपके अकाउंट में पहले से बहुत ज्यादा Followers हैं (जैसे 10K) और आप सिर्फ 1K ऑर्डर करते हैं, तो पुराने Followers Drop हो सकते हैं। ऐसे केस में Refill नहीं मिलेगा।

👉 बड़े अकाउंट्स (50K–1M) पर अगर ऑर्डर 30% से कम है तो Refill नहीं मिलेगा।
(उदाहरण: 1M Followers वाले अकाउंट पर कम से कम 300K+ एक ही Provider से ऑर्डर करें। Providers बदलकर छोटे प्रॉफिट के लिए काम न करें।)

👉 Flagged for Review या No-Post प्रोफाइल्स पर Refill नहीं मिलेगा।

👉 Refill सिर्फ उन्हीं केस में मिलेगा जब Followers End Count (Start + Order Quantity) से Drop हों और ये शर्तें पूरी हों:

Drop 10% से ज्यादा हो।

📜 Rules & Terms

𝐇𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐨 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐂𝐮𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐬,

Welcome to 𝐌𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐟𝐬𝐦𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐥.𝐢𝐧 | 𝐓𝐨𝐩𝐬𝐦𝐦.𝐢𝐧.

This is a system that generates things automatically. There can be system errors sometimes.

We don\t create accounts | This website is not for creating accounts.

We cannot manipulate any of your data since we are using a rental panel. So, if you need a refill or refund, there are certain rules.

We\ve been running this panel since 2019 and have been in the business since 2017. Rest assured, your funds are 100% safe with us, and we guarantee fair and transparent services. Below are important guidelines to keep in mind when using our services:

General Rules ✅
By making a new order or creating an account, you automatically accept our Terms & Conditions.

Make sure your Followers, Subscribers, Likes, Comments, and View Counters are not hidden. Your account must be Public, not Private, before placing an order.

If your account or posts/reels are set to Private/Hidden, or if posts are deleted, the order will be marked as Completed, and no refund will be provided.

Do not place more than one order on the same link at the same time until the first order is completed.

Do not place orders for Pornography, Politics, Extremism, or any content that stirs public opinion.

If you face any payment issue, don’t worry. Just message us on WhatsApp—your money is 100% safe with us.

Once funds are added, they cannot be refunded to your bank. Funds will remain in your topsmm.in account for service usage only.

Paytm Usage: Using our Paytm details for accepting payments on your own website is strictly prohibited.

We cannot deduct your funds without your concern. The only way is through service deductions. You can verify your balance anytime on the Payments Page.

Any attempt of fraud, fund manipulation, abuse, or threatening behavior towards our support team will result in account suspension.

Do not change accounts from Public to Private after placing an order. Such orders will be marked as completed with no refunds or cancellations.

Refill Policy 🔄
No refill will be provided if you change your username or make your account Private.

Refill applies to Order ID only, not for links. If your link doesn’t work, we cannot refill.

Condition 1: Refill is calculated as Start Count + Order Quantity = End Count. Example: If your start count is 1000 and you order 1000 followers, you are eligible for a refill if your count drops below 2000, provided it stays above the original 1000. Each order is reviewed separately.

Refill requests may be rejected if the drop is less than 10%, as our system only counts drops above 10%.

If you ordered followers and they drop, please use the Refill Button on the Orders Page or contact us on WhatsApp. Do not place a new order until the first one is completely refilled, otherwise, you may receive fewer followers.

Refill period may vary depending on updates or overload. Usually, it is processed within 24–72 hours. During Instagram updates, refill may take longer—please be patient until stability returns.

Condition 2: If your account already has a large follower base (e.g., 10K) and you order a smaller amount (e.g., 1K), old followers may drop naturally. We cannot refill in such cases. Please order your complete requirement from us so we can track and refill properly.

No refills will be provided for 50K–1M base accounts if the order is less than 30% of the existing count. Example: If you have 1M followers, you must order at least 300K+ from the same provider. Do not split orders across different providers.

No refills for Flagged for Review profiles or No-Post profiles.

Refills are guaranteed only if followers drop from the End Count (Start + Ordered Quantity), subject to these conditions:

No refill if drop is less than 10% of the order.

No refill if username is changed.

No refill if followers are mixed from other providers.

Refund Policy 💰
No refund if you place the same order on topsmm.in and another panel simultaneously for the same link. We do not support or encourage this.

If you place an order with wrong or non-working links, it will be automatically canceled and refunded to your topsmm.in wallet balance.

Partial = Refund for the undelivered portion. Example: If you order 1000 and receive 500, 50% of the payment will be refunded.

Canceled = Full refund. If an order is canceled, the full amount will be refunded to your wallet.

Refund requests for running orders may be possible for some services, but not for fast-working services.

If an order is marked Completed, you must report any issue within 24 hours for a possible solution.

For No Refill Services, no refunds or refills will be given, whether delivered, partially delivered, or marked complete.

During Instagram updates, only partial refunds may be provided. Refills may take longer.

Username switching tricks to claim refills will not work. Accounts caught attempting this will be banned immediately.

This is a multi-vendor platform; system errors may occur. Please deal with them calmly and always read our T&C.

Important Notes 📌
Do not click on potential spam notifications on Instagram about removing fake/spam accounts. If you do, and followers drop, it will not be our responsibility. No refills will be provided in such cases. Inform your clients as well. A 100% drop is not possible with our old account services.

Always keep all order IDs linked to the same account handy when requesting refills. Submit complete details to avoid delays.

For Live Views, always take screenshots with time, username, and count visible. Fake documents will result in immediate account suspension.

Behavior Policy 🚫
Any abuse, threats, or misbehavior with our support team will result in permanent account suspension.

About Our Platform ℹ️

topsmm.in is a multi-vendor reseller platform, providing services from different providers.

We operate as a mediator, reselling services with a small margin.

We are not responsible for social media account creation or content policies.

Provider details are never disclosed due to security reasons.

For any queries, please raise a support ticket or contact us on WhatsApp.

नया ऑर्डर करने या अकाउंट बनाने का मतलब है कि आप हमारी Terms & Conditions को मान चुके हैं।
